{
  "video_id": "4E_1AB1rsSw",
  "title": "How tech companies deceive you into giving up your data and privacy | Finn LÃ¼tzow-Holm Myrstad",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13400.0,
      "end_time": 15456.0,
      "text": "Do you remember when you were a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15480.0,
      "end_time": 19560.0,
      "text": "you probably had a favorite toy that was a constant companion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19800.0,
      "end_time": 21695.0,
      "text": "like Christopher Robin had Winnie the Pooh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21720.0,
      "end_time": 24520.0,
      "text": "and your imagination fueled endless adventures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25640.0,
      "end_time": 28400.0,
      "text": "What could be more innocent than that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28800.0,
      "end_time": 33600.0,
      "text": "Well, let me introduce you to my friend Cayla."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 38560.0,
      "text": "Cayla was voted toy of the year in countries around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38800.0,
      "end_time": 41656.0,
      "text": "She connects to the internet and uses speech recognition technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41680.0,
      "end_time": 43816.0,
      "text": "to answer your child&#39;s questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43840.0,
      "end_time": 45800.0,
      "text": "respond just like a friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46920.0,
      "end_time": 50576.0,
      "text": "But the power doesn&#39;t lie with your child&#39;s imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50600.0,
      "end_time": 55136.0,
      "text": "It actually lies with the company harvesting masses of personal information"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55160.0,
      "end_time": 60696.0,
      "text": "while your family is innocently chatting away in the safety of their home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60720.0,
      "end_time": 63199.0,
      "text": "a dangerously false sense of security."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64840.0,
      "end_time": 67496.0,
      "text": "This case sounded alarm bells for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67520.0,
      "end_time": 70720.0,
      "text": "as it is my job to protect consumers&#39; rights in my country."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71800.0,
      "end_time": 75295.0,
      "text": "And with billions of devices such as cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75320.0,
      "end_time": 80416.0,
      "text": "energy meters and even vacuum cleaners expected to come online by 2020,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 80440.0,
      "end_time": 84376.0,
      "text": "we thought this was a case worth investigating further."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84400.0,
      "end_time": 86296.0,
      "text": "Because what was Cayla doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86320.0,
      "end_time": 88856.0,
      "text": "with all the interesting things she was learning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88880.0,
      "end_time": 92520.0,
      "text": "Did she have another friend she was loyal to and shared her information with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93640.0,
      "end_time": 96416.0,
      "text": "Yes, you guessed right. She did."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96440.0,
      "end_time": 98536.0,
      "text": "In order to play with Cayla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 98560.0,
      "end_time": 101560.0,
      "text": "you need to download an app to access all her features."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102280.0,
      "end_time": 106120.0,
      "text": "Parents must consent to the terms being changed without notice."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107280.0,
      "end_time": 111560.0,
      "text": "The recordings of the child, her friends and family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 111800.0,
      "end_time": 113390.0,
      "text": "can be used for targeted advertising."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 114800.0,
      "end_time": 119390.0,
      "text": "And all this information can be shared with unnamed third parties."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 119760.0,
      "end_time": 121880.0,
      "text": "Enough? Not quite."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 122880.0,
      "end_time": 127176.0,
      "text": "Anyone with a smartphone can connect to Cayla"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 127200.0,
      "end_time": 128800.0,
      "text": "within a certain distance."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 129560.0,
      "end_time": 134136.0,
      "text": "When we confronted the company that made and programmed Cayla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 134160.0,
      "end_time": 136416.0,
      "text": "they issued a series of statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 136440.0,
      "end_time": 140560.0,
      "text": "that one had to be an IT expert in order to breach the security."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 142390.0,
      "end_time": 145959.0,
      "text": "Shall we fact-check that statement and live hack Cayla together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149920.0,
      "end_time": 151119.0,
      "text": "Here she is."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 152200.0,
      "end_time": 155576.0,
      "text": "Cayla is equipped with a Bluetooth device"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 155600.0,
      "end_time": 157816.0,
      "text": "which can transmit up to 60 feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157840.0,
      "end_time": 160456.0,
      "text": "a bit less if there&#39;s a wall between."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160480.0,
      "end_time": 165775.0,
      "text": "That means I, or any stranger, can connect to the doll"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 165800.0,
      "end_time": 169536.0,
      "text": "while being outside the room where Cayla and her friends are."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 169560.0,
      "end_time": 171736.0,
      "text": "And to illustrate this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 171760.0,
      "end_time": 173896.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to turn Cayla on now."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 173920.0,
      "end_time": 175720.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see, one, two, three."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "There. She&#39;s on. And I asked a colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 179400.0,
      "end_time": 181136.0,
      "text": "to stand outside with his smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 181160.0,
      "end_time": 182400.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s connected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 183320.0,
      "end_time": 185416.0,
      "text": "and to make this a bit creepier ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 185440.0,
      "end_time": 189496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 189520.0,
      "end_time": 194440.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s see what kids could hear Cayla say in the safety of their room."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195920.0,
      "end_time": 198815.0,
      "text": "Man: Hi. My name is Cayla. What is yours?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 198840.0,
      "end_time": 200160.0,
      "text": "Finn Myrstad: Uh, Finn."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 200960.0,
      "end_time": 202256.0,
      "text": "Man: Is your mom close by?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 202280.0,
      "end_time": 203760.0,
      "text": "FM: Uh, no, she&#39;s in the store."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 204680.0,
      "end_time": 207560.0,
      "text": "Man: Ah. Do you want to come out and play with me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 207800.0,
      "end_time": 208560.0,
      "text": "FM: That&#39;s a great idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 209720.0,
      "end_time": 210920.0,
      "text": "Man: Ah, great."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 212480.0,
      "end_time": 214616.0,
      "text": "FM: I&#39;m going to turn Cayla off now."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 214640.0,
      "end_time": 215839.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 221816.0,
      "text": "We needed no password"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 221840.0,
      "end_time": 225400.0,
      "text": "or to circumvent any other type of security to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 226440.0,
      "end_time": 230256.0,
      "text": "We published a report in 20 countries around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230280.0,
      "end_time": 233256.0,
      "text": "exposing this significant security flaw"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 233280.0,
      "end_time": 235400.0,
      "text": "and many other problematic issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236000.0,
      "end_time": 237240.0,
      "text": "So what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237840.0,
      "end_time": 239480.0,
      "text": "Cayla was banned in Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 240480.0,
      "end_time": 243696.0,
      "text": "taken off the shelves by Amazon and Wal-Mart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 243720.0,
      "end_time": 246776.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s now peacefully resting"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246800.0,
      "end_time": 250256.0,
      "text": "at the German Spy Museum in Berlin."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 250280.0,
      "end_time": 253560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253800.0,
      "end_time": 257376.0,
      "text": "However, Cayla was also for sale in stores around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257399.0,
      "end_time": 260976.0,
      "text": "for more than a year after we published our report."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 261000.0,
      "end_time": 265256.0,
      "text": "What we uncovered is that there are few rules to protect us"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 265280.0,
      "end_time": 268640.0,
      "text": "and the ones we have are not being properly enforced."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 270000.0,
      "end_time": 273856.0,
      "text": "We need to get the security and privacy of these devices right"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273880.0,
      "end_time": 276736.0,
      "text": "before they enter the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 276760.0,
      "end_time": 280736.0,
      "text": "because what is the point of locking a house with a key"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 280760.0,
      "end_time": 283680.0,
      "text": "if anyone can enter it through a connected device?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 285640.0,
      "end_time": 288936.0,
      "text": "You may well think, \"This will not happen to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 288960.0,
      "end_time": 291560.0,
      "text": "I will just stay away from these flawed devices.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 292600.0,
      "end_time": 294656.0,
      "text": "But that won&#39;t keep you safe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 297856.0,
      "text": "because simply by connecting to the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 297880.0,
      "end_time": 302456.0,
      "text": "you are put in an impossible take-it-or-leave-it position."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 302480.0,
      "end_time": 303680.0,
      "text": "Let me show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 304400.0,
      "end_time": 307496.0,
      "text": "Like most of you, I have dozens of apps on my phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 307520.0,
      "end_time": 310376.0,
      "text": "and used properly, they can make our lives easier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 310400.0,
      "end_time": 312840.0,
      "text": "more convenient and maybe even healthier."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 313960.0,
      "end_time": 317479.0,
      "text": "But have we been lulled into a false sense of security?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 318600.0,
      "end_time": 321400.0,
      "text": "It starts simply by ticking a box."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 321880.0,
      "end_time": 323656.0,
      "text": "Yes, we say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 323680.0,
      "end_time": 325120.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve read the terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 327240.0,
      "end_time": 330280.0,
      "text": "But have you really read the terms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 331200.0,
      "end_time": 333496.0,
      "text": "Are you sure they didn&#39;t look too long"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 333520.0,
      "end_time": 335575.0,
      "text": "and your phone was running out of battery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 335600.0,
      "end_time": 338816.0,
      "text": "and the last time you tried they were impossible to understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 338840.0,
      "end_time": 340679.0,
      "text": "and you needed to use the service now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 341840.0,
      "end_time": 345496.0,
      "text": "And now, the power imbalance is established,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 345520.0,
      "end_time": 349176.0,
      "text": "because we have agreed to our personal information"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 349200.0,
      "end_time": 352320.0,
      "text": "being gathered and used on a scale we could never imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 353640.0,
      "end_time": 357336.0,
      "text": "This is why my colleagues and I decided to take a deeper look at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 357360.0,
      "end_time": 360696.0,
      "text": "We set out to read the terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 360720.0,
      "end_time": 363416.0,
      "text": "of popular apps on an average phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 363440.0,
      "end_time": 367176.0,
      "text": "And to show the world how unrealistic it is"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367200.0,
      "end_time": 370416.0,
      "text": "to expect consumers to actually read the terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 370440.0,
      "end_time": 371936.0,
      "text": "we printed them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 371960.0,
      "end_time": 373799.0,
      "text": "more than 900 pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 374800.0,
      "end_time": 378400.0,
      "text": "and sat down in our office and read them out loud ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 379800.0,
      "end_time": 382336.0,
      "text": "streaming the experiment live on our websites."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 382360.0,
      "end_time": 384896.0,
      "text": "As you can see, it took quite a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 384920.0,
      "end_time": 389336.0,
      "text": "It took us 31 hours, 49 minutes and 11 seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 389360.0,
      "end_time": 391936.0,
      "text": "to read the terms on an average phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 391960.0,
      "end_time": 396335.0,
      "text": "That is longer than a movie marathon of the \"Harry Potter\" movies"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 396360.0,
      "end_time": 398856.0,
      "text": "and the \"Godfather\" movies combined."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 398880.0,
      "end_time": 400280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 401600.0,
      "end_time": 403536.0,
      "text": "And reading is one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 403560.0,
      "end_time": 405536.0,
      "text": "Understanding is another story."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 405560.0,
      "end_time": 409136.0,
      "text": "That would have taken us much, much longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 409160.0,
      "end_time": 410936.0,
      "text": "And this is a real problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 410960.0,
      "end_time": 414176.0,
      "text": "because companies have argued for 20 to 30 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 414200.0,
      "end_time": 417256.0,
      "text": "against regulating the internet better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417280.0,
      "end_time": 420440.0,
      "text": "because users have consented to the terms and conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 422520.0,
      "end_time": 424496.0,
      "text": "As we&#39;ve shown with this experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 424520.0,
      "end_time": 427400.0,
      "text": "achieving informed consent is close to impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429800.0,
      "end_time": 432604.0,
      "text": "Do you think it&#39;s fair to put the burden of responsibility on the consumer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 434000.0,
      "end_time": 435736.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 435760.0,
      "end_time": 438856.0,
      "text": "I think we should demand less take-it-or-leave-it"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 438880.0,
      "end_time": 442560.0,
      "text": "and more understandable terms before we agree to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 442800.0,
      "end_time": 443616.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 443640.0,
      "end_time": 444840.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 448200.0,
      "end_time": 453800.0,
      "text": "Now, I would like to tell you a story about love."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 454800.0,
      "end_time": 457616.0,
      "text": "Some of the world&#39;s most popular apps are dating apps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 457640.0,
      "end_time": 462280.0,
      "text": "an industry now worth more than, or close to, three billion dollars a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 463160.0,
      "end_time": 467336.0,
      "text": "And of course, we&#39;re OK sharing our intimate details"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 467360.0,
      "end_time": 468600.0,
      "text": "with our other half."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 469240.0,
      "end_time": 471216.0,
      "text": "But who else is snooping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 471240.0,
      "end_time": 474176.0,
      "text": "saving and sharing our information"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 474200.0,
      "end_time": 475840.0,
      "text": "while we are baring our souls?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476520.0,
      "end_time": 478719.0,
      "text": "My team and I decided to investigate this."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 480920.0,
      "end_time": 483936.0,
      "text": "And in order to understand the issue from all angles"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 483960.0,
      "end_time": 486200.0,
      "text": "and to truly do a thorough job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 487400.0,
      "end_time": 489376.0,
      "text": "I realized I had to download"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 489400.0,
      "end_time": 492840.0,
      "text": "one of the world&#39;s most popular dating apps myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 494440.0,
      "end_time": 496736.0,
      "text": "So I went home to my wife ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 496760.0,
      "end_time": 498695.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 498720.0,
      "end_time": 500376.0,
      "text": "who I had just married."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 500400.0,
      "end_time": 505150.0,
      "text": "\"Is it OK if I establish a profile on a very popular dating app"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 505400.0,
      "end_time": 506936.0,
      "text": "for purely scientific purposes?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 506960.0,
      "end_time": 508816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 508840.0,
      "end_time": 510335.0,
      "text": "This is what we found."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 510360.0,
      "end_time": 514336.0,
      "text": "Hidden behind the main menu was a preticked box"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 514360.0,
      "end_time": 520416.0,
      "text": "that gave the dating company access to all my personal pictures on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 520440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523296.00000000006,
      "text": "in my case more than 2,000 of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 523320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525440.0,
      "text": "and some were quite personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 526400.0,
      "end_time": 528616.0,
      "text": "And to make matters worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 528640.0,
      "end_time": 530696.0,
      "text": "when we read the terms and conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 530720.0,
      "end_time": 532960.0,
      "text": "we discovered the following,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 532120.0,
      "end_time": 535240.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to need to take out my reading glasses for this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 536400.0,
      "end_time": 539336.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to read it for you, because this is complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 539360.0,
      "end_time": 540560.0,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 541440.0,
      "end_time": 542976.0,
      "text": "\"By posting content\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 543000.0,
      "end_time": 544976.0,
      "text": "and content refers to your pictures, chat"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 545000.0,
      "end_time": 547216.0,
      "text": "and other interactions in the dating service --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 547240.0,
      "end_time": 548496.0,
      "text": "\"as a part of the service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 548520.0,
      "end_time": 550496.0,
      "text": "you automatically grant to the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 550520.0,
      "end_time": 552696.0,
      "text": "its affiliates, licensees and successors"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 552720.0,
      "end_time": 556336.0,
      "text": "an irrevocable\" -- which means you can&#39;t change your mind --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 556360.0,
      "end_time": 559136.0,
      "text": "\"perpetual\" -- which means forever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 559160.0,
      "end_time": 562550.0,
      "text": "\"nonexclusive, transferrable, sublicensable, fully paid-up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 562800.0,
      "end_time": 564776.0,
      "text": "worldwide right and license to use, copy, store, perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 564800.0,
      "end_time": 566136.0,
      "text": "display, reproduce, record,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 566160.0,
      "end_time": 568376.0,
      "text": "play, adapt, modify and distribute the content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 568400.0,
      "end_time": 570336.0,
      "text": "prepare derivative works of the content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 570360.0,
      "end_time": 572376.0,
      "text": "or incorporate the content into other works"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 572400.0,
      "end_time": 575456.0,
      "text": "and grant and authorize sublicenses of the foregoing in any media"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 575480.0,
      "end_time": 577400.0,
      "text": "now known or hereafter created.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 580640.0,
      "end_time": 584456.0,
      "text": "That basically means that all your dating history"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 584480.0,
      "end_time": 589560.0,
      "text": "and everything related to it can be used for any purpose for all time."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 590520.0,
      "end_time": 595496.0,
      "text": "Just imagine your children seeing your sassy dating photos"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 595520.0,
      "end_time": 598790.0,
      "text": "in a birth control ad 20 years from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 600400.0,
      "end_time": 601616.0,
      "text": "But seriously, though --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 601640.0,
      "end_time": 603240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 604880.0,
      "end_time": 607240.0,
      "text": "what might these commercial practices mean to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 608320.0,
      "end_time": 610560.0,
      "text": "For example, financial loss:"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 611480.0,
      "end_time": 613176.0,
      "text": "based on your web browsing history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 613200.0,
      "end_time": 616160.0,
      "text": "algorithms might decide whether you will get a mortgage or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 616840.0,
      "end_time": 618320.0,
      "text": "Subconscious manipulation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 619560.0,
      "end_time": 623256.0,
      "text": "companies can analyze your emotions based on your photos and chats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 623280.0,
      "end_time": 626536.0,
      "text": "targeting you with ads when you are at your most vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 626560.0,
      "end_time": 628550.0,
      "text": "Discrimination:"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 631960.0,
      "text": "a fitness app can sell your data to a health insurance company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 631120.0,
      "end_time": 634176.0,
      "text": "preventing you from getting coverage in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 634200.0,
      "end_time": 636720.0,
      "text": "All of this is happening in the world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 637800.0,
      "end_time": 641136.0,
      "text": "But of course, not all uses of data are malign."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 641160.0,
      "end_time": 643136.0,
      "text": "Some are just flawed or need more work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 643160.0,
      "end_time": 644680.0,
      "text": "and some are truly great."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 647560.0,
      "end_time": 651256.0,
      "text": "And there is some good news as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 651280.0,
      "end_time": 654576.0,
      "text": "The dating companies changed their policies globally"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 654600.0,
      "end_time": 656280.0,
      "text": "after we filed a legal complaint."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 657720.0,
      "end_time": 660416.0,
      "text": "But organizations such as mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 660440.0,
      "end_time": 663416.0,
      "text": "that fight for consumers&#39; rights can&#39;t be everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 663440.0,
      "end_time": 665976.0,
      "text": "Nor can consumers fix this on their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 666000.0,
      "end_time": 669576.0,
      "text": "because if we know that something innocent we said"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 669600.0,
      "end_time": 671560.0,
      "text": "will come back to haunt us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 671800.0,
      "end_time": 672976.0,
      "text": "we will stop speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 673000.0,
      "end_time": 676376.0,
      "text": "If we know that we are being watched and monitored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 676400.0,
      "end_time": 678496.0,
      "text": "we will change our behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 678520.0,
      "end_time": 682415.0,
      "text": "And if we can&#39;t control who has our data and how it is being used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 682440.0,
      "end_time": 684280.0,
      "text": "we have lost the control of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 686400.0,
      "end_time": 689896.0,
      "text": "The stories I have told you today are not random examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 689920.0,
      "end_time": 691695.0,
      "text": "They are everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 691720.0,
      "end_time": 694576.0,
      "text": "and they are a sign that things need to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 694600.0,
      "end_time": 696696.0,
      "text": "And how can we achieve that change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 696720.0,
      "end_time": 702296.0,
      "text": "Well, companies need to realize that by prioritizing privacy and security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 702320.0,
      "end_time": 705280.0,
      "text": "they can build trust and loyalty to their users."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 706520.0,
      "end_time": 709616.0,
      "text": "Governments must create a safer internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 709640.0,
      "end_time": 712520.0,
      "text": "by ensuring enforcement and up-to-date rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 713400.0,
      "end_time": 715616.0,
      "text": "And us, the citizens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 715640.0,
      "end_time": 717456.0,
      "text": "We can use our voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 717480.0,
      "end_time": 722576.0,
      "text": "to remind the world that technology can only truly benefit society"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 722600.0,
      "end_time": 725200.0,
      "text": "if it respects basic rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 725720.0,
      "end_time": 727296.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 727320.0,
      "end_time": 731400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}